      OPTS="--bindir=/usr/games"
  ESTIMATE="84"
     SHORT="ggz is the GGZ Gaming Zone for online gaming."
      LONG="
ggz is the GGZ Gaming Zone (GGZ) is an Internet gaming center.
Players login and sit at tables where they can play 
their favorite games and chat with other players.
GGZ can support multiple rooms with varying skill levels.
This profile also installs documentation for ggz.
